rows.label: qst101201_msg0001
rows.name: Mo! Why isn't it growing bigger, mo?

rows.label: qst101201_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm trying to grow new vegetables
with the seeds my grandma left me.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0003
rows.name:
But the vegetables are
too delicate, they won't
grow bigger at all, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0004
rows.name:
I really want to give them
lots of fertilizer, but...

rows.label: qst101201_msg0005
rows.name:
I've been so focused on development
that I don't have any vegetables to
sell, so I'm completely broke, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0006
rows.name:
I guess I have to give up, mo...
Grandma, I'm sorry, mo...

rows.label: qst101201_msg0007
rows.name:
You'll help me, mo?
Mo! I'm so happy, mo!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0008
rows.name:
When the new vegetables are
ready, I'll let you be the
first to eat them, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0009
rows.name:
If you find something that
could be used as fertilizer,
let me know, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0010
rows.name:
If it's very nutritious, a small
amount will be enough, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0101
rows.name:
Will you give me some fertilizer,
mo? Different things have
different nutrients, mo.

rows.label: qst101201_msg0110
rows.name:
Still not enough nutrients, mo~
I'm waiting for fertilizer, mo!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0120
rows.name:
The nutrients are perfect
now, mo! Thank you, mo!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0121
rows.name:
It should grow bigger overnight, mo!
Come back after a good sleep, mo!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0201
rows.name:
Thanks for your help, mo! Lots of
fertilizer, lots of nutrients, mo!

rows.label: qst101201_msg0202
rows.name:
It should grow bigger overnight, mo!
Come back after a good sleep, mo!
